<Docs title="Installation" description="Install and package Dep Beacon locally.">
  <h1>Installation</h1>
  <p>
    Dep Beacon is developed as a pnpm and Turbo monorepo. Use Node 22 or newer for the smoothest local experience.
  </p>

  <h2>Workspace setup</h2>
  <pre><code>pnpm install
pnpm run build
pnpm run typecheck
pnpm run test
pnpm run lint</code></pre>

  <h2>Package the extension</h2>
  <pre><code>pnpm run package:extension</code></pre>
  <p>
    The VSIX is written to `packages/vscode-dep-beacon/dep-beacon.vsix`.
  </p>

  <h2>Run the docs site</h2>
  <pre><code>pnpm --filter @santi020k/dep-beacon-docs dev</code></pre>
</Docs>
